Module com.erudika.para.core
Package com.erudika.para.core.annotations

Annotation Type Documented

  • @Target({METHOD,FIELD})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface Documented
    A generic annotation intended to be used for attaching documentation metadata to the getter methods of configuration properties.
    Author:
    Alex Bogdanovski [alex@erudika.com]

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      String category  
      String description  
      String identifier  
      String type  
      String value  

    • Element Detail

      • category

        String category
        Returns:
        the category which this property is part of.
        Default:
        "main"

      • description

        String description
        Returns:
        basic description of the config property.
        Default:
        ""

      • type

        String type
        Returns:
        the data type of the config value.
        Default:
        "string"

      • value

        String value
        Returns:
        a default or suggested value.
        Default:
        ""

      • identifier

        String identifier
        Returns:
        the config property key (identifier).
        Default:
        ""
